WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:06.900 --> 00:00:09.700
 Good afternoon. Campers on Vlieland are worried ... 

00:00:09.700 --> 00:00:14.100
 about safety at camping Stortemelk. 

00:00:14.100 --> 00:00:17.700
 Last night, dozens of tents fanned out. 

00:00:17.700 --> 00:00:21.400
 Witnesses call it a miracle that bad accidents have not occurred. 

00:00:21.400 --> 00:00:26.000
 I would have been very worried if it had been the pop festival this weekend. 

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:29.500
 We are all experienced campers ... 

00:00:29.500 --> 00:00:32.500
 and know many people here where we can go. 

00:00:32.500 --> 00:00:37.800
 But what if this had happened to the thousands at the Great White Open ... 

00:00:37.800 --> 00:00:40.200
 then I am very worried. 

00:00:40.200 --> 00:00:44.100
 The management of the campsite says in a response ... 

00:00:44.100 --> 00:00:47.900
 that enough has been done for the campers. 

00:00:47.900 --> 00:00:51.700
 A traffic chaos this morning in Leeuwarden South ... 

00:00:51.700 --> 00:00:56.600
 due to defective traffic lights at Goutum. 

00:00:56.600 --> 00:01:01.400
 From the Werpsterhoek to beyond the Van Harinxma bridge it was one long traffic jam. 

00:01:01.400 --> 00:01:06.000
 The traffic at Goutum and on Algraweg was also completely fixed. 

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:11.500
 The crowds were exacerbated by work on the bicycle tunnel at 't Oostergoplein. 

00:01:11.500 --> 00:01:14.600
 A roadway was closed without consultation. 

00:01:14.600 --> 00:01:20.600
 You need to report something to the police. We will address the builder. 

00:01:20.600 --> 00:01:25.700
 That interference was a coincidence, wasn't it? -Yes, that was absolutely not foreseen. 

00:01:25.700 --> 00:01:31.700
 That also made it an unfortunate coincidence. 

00:01:31.700 --> 00:01:35.400
 At Kornwerderzand on the Afsluitdijk, only four schools are allowed ... 

00:01:35.400 --> 00:01:38.500
 teaching kite surfing. 

00:01:38.500 --> 00:01:42.400
 The four have been agreed with the municipality and Rijkswaterstaat. 

00:01:42.400 --> 00:01:48.500
 There can be no more than 55 students at the same time. Kite surfing must become safer this way. 

00:01:48.500 --> 00:01:53.800
 A recent fatal accident with a kite surfer was the reason for the agreements. 

00:01:53.800 --> 00:01:57.800
 For the surfing schools it also plays a role that German competitors ... 

00:01:57.800 --> 00:02:01.300
 may no longer just teach there. 

00:02:01.300 --> 00:02:07.600
 In Balk, fake weapons were seized that people had won at the fair. 

00:02:07.600 --> 00:02:13.100
 Someone saw two boys with a gun in a playground and informed the police. 

00:02:13.100 --> 00:02:17.200
 After seizure it turned out to be a fake gun. 

00:02:17.200 --> 00:02:22.900
 The exhibitor handed them in and the police asked owners to do the same. 

00:02:22.900 --> 00:02:29.900
 The trial with the Waddentaxi for children in special education is being discontinued. 

00:02:29.900 --> 00:02:35.100
 The majority of Ameland municipal councils do not have 36,000 euros left for it. 

00:02:35.100 --> 00:02:41.400
 Parents are disappointed and will do their best to keep the water taxi. 

00:02:41.400 --> 00:02:48.000
 Citizens of Boarnsterhim are dissatisfied with the municipal reorganization plans. 

00:02:48.000 --> 00:02:54.100
 These posters were displayed in Aldeboarn. The plans were announced last week. 

00:02:54.100 --> 00:02:57.400
 There were consultation evenings beforehand. 

00:02:57.400 --> 00:03:01.000
 The residents now feel that their opinion has not been taken into account. 

00:03:01.000 --> 00:03:03.900
 I thought: I'll just post a note. 

00:03:03.900 --> 00:03:08.600
 We have to indicate that we are not being fooled by this. 

00:03:08.600 --> 00:03:13.000
 The Municipal Executive wants to divide the municipality into three parts. 

00:03:13.000 --> 00:03:19.100
 Today the first Frisian Vocational College started at OSG Sevenwolden in Heerenveen. 

00:03:19.100 --> 00:03:26.000
 A training where young talent is trained in 6 years to become a professional or professional woman. 

00:03:26.000 --> 00:03:32.000
 The morning starts immediately with practical lessons: devising and making a tool box. 

00:03:32.000 --> 00:03:37.400
 VMBO, MBO and the business community work together in the Vakcollege. 

00:03:37.400 --> 00:03:42.200
 Companies are looking for students with better technical knowledge than VMBO students. 

00:03:42.200 --> 00:03:45.000
 Motivation is really a problem ... 

00:03:45.000 --> 00:03:49.100
 to judge by what we hear from the internship companies. 

00:03:49.100 --> 00:03:52.700
 The knowledge is highly generalized at VMBO. 

00:03:52.700 --> 00:03:58.400
 The emphasis is on technical directions. Service courses will come later. 

00:03:58.400 --> 00:04:03.700
 It is already a successful concept at 60 Dutch schools. 

00:04:03.700 --> 00:04:09.200
 The weather: more clouds tonight with a chance of rain showers. Around 11 degrees. 

00:04:09.200 --> 00:04:12.900
 In the wadden region a moderate to fairly strong northwest wind. 

00:04:12.900 --> 00:04:18.000
 Tomorrow a lot of sun, but also clouds. Temperatures around 19 degrees. 

00:04:18.000 --> 00:04:21.700
 Moderate wind from the north to northwest. 

00:04:21.700 --> 00:04:26.100
 This was the short news. At 6 o'clock we are back with more and different news. 

00:04:26.100 --> 00:04:28.200
 See you later. 

